Package: gammaSpec
Type: Package
Title: Analyse Gamma Spectra of NaI(Tl) Scintillation Radiation Detectors
Description: A minimal package to import and plot SPE files recorded by
    ORTEC NaI(Tl) Scintillation Radiation Detectors with a digiBASE 
    Digital Multichannel Analyser as well as to derive the external wet 
    gamma dose rate.
Version: 0.1.0.9100
Date: 2017-05-12
Authors@R: c(
    person("Christoph", "Burow", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "christoph.burow@uni-koeln.de"),
    person("Franz", "Hartung", role = "ctb", comment = "Physics consulting")
    )
Maintainer: Christoph Burow <christoph.burow@uni-koeln.de>
Description: A Collection of Functions to Analyse Gamma Spectrums.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/tzerk/gammaSpec
BugReports: https://github.com/tzerk/gammaSpec/issues
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.2)
Suggests:
    shiny (>= 1.03),
    testthat (>= 1.02)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
